            <h1 itemprop="headline">Hackers exploited 0-day, not 2018 bug, to mass-wipe My Book Live devices [Updated]</h1>
            <h2 itemprop="description">Western Digital removed code that would have prevented the wiping of petabytes of data.</h2>
